<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-21-0381 </DOCNO><TEXT>In this overview paper, the author attempts to identify and describe someof the common threads that tie together work in reasoning about knowledgein such diverse fields as philosophy, economics, linguistics, artificialintelligence, and theoretical computer science. He briefly discussessome of the more recent work, particularly in computer science, and suggestssome lines for future research.</TEXT></DOC>